Class TurnKinectAbs

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoSpreadsheetCommand, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.NamedSendable, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Sendable

    public class TurnKinectAbs
extends TurnGyroAbs
    Turns to an angle using the Gyro; The Kinect chooses the direction. The angle is relative to the starting angle of the robot. The height of the right and left hands is used to choose the direction.
